description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'Quick & INTENSE 10-minute Cycling Workout | THE JOURNEY ENCORE!' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Nightclub Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: If you only have ten minutes for a workout, this is the one for you!!! This 10 minutes is going to take you on a journey! This ride will take you through the entire spectrum of resistance and speed so you can increase your muscular strength and endurance, plus improve your cardiovascular endurance! This is also the perfect workout finisher after any cycling or strength workout!

This song, The Journey, was created just for this ride!! One of our very own amazing butt-kickers, Peter Spero, along with his band Black Diamond Sessions wrote this just for us! 

Make sure to check out Peter: https://open.spotify.com/artist/2ohEtPcrG5VbGdZCeDWBk8?si=xZWNnSWwTBWaOX6vUycqwA
and Black Diamond Sessions: https://open.spotify.com/artist/7heAiD37FywViSeH77Gvd0?si=ruEB7uaKRvKISxZfXll8rg

IMPORTANT! The RPMs noted throughout the ride are just a range! Make sure to ride where you feel comfortable! That may be above or below the range indicated.
